      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "wait sorry i think i got confused with the explanation. u said to go down a minor third to find the relative major of eb major? i thought the relative major and minor just share the same key signature. can u just walk me through the actual steps using the circle itself? like, do i move clockwise or counterclockwise?",
